title: Kiss Woman Man Light Skin Tone Medium Skin Tone

The smooth, rounded edges of their faces and the subtle blush tones add a warmth and intimacy unique to Apple's emoji design. This emoji beautifully symbolizes love, romance, and affection between a couple on Apple devices.
